label: Lumi LM-S4ZW (C-L)

info_overview:
4 Button Z-Wave Switch: 2 lights and 2 buttons for up/down blinds control.

  • Operating Voltage: 100 - 240V/50Hz
  • Operating Temperature: 0 - 50ÂºC

info_inclusion: Touch and hold any key on the panel for more than 5 seconds. All indication lights will blinks in blue. At this point release the key, the touch panel will start inclusion process.
